---
// DigitalStone.astro
// Block 3: Digital Stone
// Grid Layout: 12-Column Grid | Split 5/5 with 2-Col Gutter
// Container Physics: [Height: 100vh] | [Scroll: Snap-Point]
---

<section id="digital-stone" class="min-h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-center p-4 md:p-8 snap-start relative border-t border-surface/30 section-pt">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full flex flex-col justify-center">
    
    <!-- Problem Keyword (H2 | VR3) -->
    <h2 class="text-xs md:text-sm font-body font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent mb-4 text-center md:text-left">
      The solution to your technical debt
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 mt-4">
      
      <!-- Column 1: The Narrative -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center">
        <!-- The Solution (H3 | VR2) -->
        <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight text-text-heading mb-6">
          Own your stack with a Portable Digital Bedrock.
        </h3>
        
        <!-- Context Copy -->
        <p class="text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          I design and replace "sandy foundations" with portable, open-source solid web architectures.
        </p>
        <p class="text-text-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          There's no reason to keep wasting money, time, and resources fixing something that was born broken.
        </p>
        
        <div class="text-text-heading font-medium text-lg p-6 bg-surface/50 border-l-4 border-accent">
          <p>Your infrastructure should be a reliable and scalable asset, not a monthly liability.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Spacer (2-Col Gutter) -->
      <div class="hidden md:block md:col-span-2"></div>

      <!-- Column 2: The Sovereign Traits -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5 flex flex-col justify-center bg-surface/20 p-8 md:p-10 border border-surface/50">
        <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-text-heading mb-8 uppercase tracking-wide">
          What's a Portable Digital Bedrock?
        </h3>
        
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-lg list-none p-0 m-0">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-text-body">Solution tailored to your business.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-text-body">Scalable digital architectures.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-text-body">Cost-efficient providers.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-text-body">Zero SaaS platform captivity.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-text-body">Portable, open-source foundations.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent mr-3 shrink-0 mt-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-text-body text-text-heading font-medium">100% asset ownership.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
